snippet.title: Super Indie Karts x Read Only Memories 1080p
snippet.description:
Here Comes A Newly Updated RaceTrack!! - It's Genus Market from Read Only Memories!

Super Indie Karts is a '90s style kart racer available in Early Access on Steam (for Windows and Mac) and OUYA featuring racetrack and kart crossovers with a heap of super Indie Games. http://store.steampowered.com/app/323670/

Read Only Memories is an adventure game that starts in December, 2064AD. Your life as a struggling journalist is interrupted by the world’s first sapient robot, a ROM named Turing. Explore the world of Neo-San Francisco, befriend the locals, and decide how to approach your encounters. Available for Steam (for Windows, Mac OS X, SteamOS and Linux), you can find more info at http://store.steampowered.com/app/330820/
